author: Amai Ta. Yume
text:
Rushia was so energetic from the beginning to the end. Everything was happiness, bliss (and rage) that it kept me watching a lot and continue to hear your voice when I'm busy. I still love her group's Halloween music. Couldn't stop listening to it!

Thank you for the fandeads who helped her along the way. It was way too forgiving, but as a result, Rushia could fall as much as she likes and still made it to the next round. It was so fun and so funny at the same time! <3 

Take care of your health Rushia! I love this stream and I love Rushia alot just as much (or more) as everyone! <3 <3 

PS: It was cute when she just came back a bit to thank the remaining super chatto! <3
